            "nethysUrl": "https://2e.aonprd.com/Monsters.aspx?ID=757",
            "recallKnowledgeText": "Recall Knowledge - Beast : DC 19",
            "sidebarText": "<h3 class=\"title\"><img alt=\"Sidebar - Additional Lore\" title=\"Sidebar - Additional Lore\" style=\"height:20px; padding:2px 10px 0px 2px\" src=\"Images\\Icons\\Sidebar_2_AdditionalLore.png\"> Peryton Flocks</h3>On rare occasions, a peryton flock forms at the lead of an alpha female. It lasts until the alpha makes a mistake that erodes her perceived power. Then the rest of the flock tears her apart.",
            "source": {
                "value": "Bestiary 2 pg. 197"
